text: The positive social factor is not intelligence promotion but intelligence inhibition. That's where the social order finds its highest purpose. Thus, intelligence escape (run-away, true philosophy, renaissance, industrial revolution) happens when the social order is shattered. ...

... Warring states, competitive city-states, ragged patchworks where arms-races can assemble themselves and liberate human intellectual capability from homeostatic social duty. Chinese social order was too well-assembled to let the monster escape. It had to be torn open.
We'll see.
